      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the caution but i already take a multivitamin and i feel like i'm running really low. if i just do it for like 10 or 14 days to \"front-load\" it, isn't that basically how some doctors suggest doing it to correct a deficiency? i don't really have time for a blood test right now so i just want to know if doing it for two weeks is a common way to fix it quickly.",
